top_projects.name: WatchPost
top_projects.description: WatchPost is an automated LinkedIn post creation tool that creates LinkedIn posts for you based on your activity on GitHub. It goes through your repos checks what happened in the last 24 hours and based on that writes you a LinkedIn post talking about what you have been up to since the last post.
